{"tid":2058154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀：或應更早提醒特首撤回修例","createTime":"2020-06-10T02:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T08:52:59.000Z","uid":54800,"like":54,"dislike":379,"uniUserReply":136,"replies":[{"pid":"42c927681e5d8f5186202223e777bf98fb22dc51","tid":2058154,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"反修例事件的示威已持續一年，身兼行會成員的新民黨立法會議員葉劉淑儀認同，每人都要汲取教訓。<br />\n<br />\n她出席一個電台節目後說，特別是身兼行會成員的立法會議員，當時已就修訂《逃犯條例》盡了所有責任支持政府，初期市民對修例沒有興趣，及後才對修例感到恐懼，認為或許應更早提醒行政長官，在去年6月9日前就撤回條例。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531217-20200610.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531217-20200610.htm&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=d93c9ec5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531217-20200610.htm&h=a3a5b74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531217-20200610.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3b0cc38fb01b37b6e7e2e86e1b439f52b631972a","tid":2058154,"uid":88743,"like":223,"dislike":1,"score":222,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"又消費妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec4e1bae045a487f034d7082a8488040e93c901","tid":2058154,"uid":108201,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:57:07.000Z","msg":"驚呀，唔好退縮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2348b8112a8fbb686a556ab317b967132efac9b","tid":2058154,"uid":42429,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"姐姐好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56a9fd27e6c8200e916d87e5ac3a6393c88c47a","tid":2058154,"uid":214502,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"提醒會聽咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif